Dialogs.Dialog: It's been a while. I'm not complaining though.
What do you think of Rinko's house after this long time？
Welcome. Well, you already know how it work.
Come, hurry and get in. Have a seat at the table.
Here you go. Make yourself at home.
You... seem at home in this room, don't you？
I'm sure that's true. There are people, you know, who go to anyone's house and become as comfortable as family in five seconds.
I wonder if I feel at home that much...
It's nice to relax at home like this, isn't it？
Yeah. I'm a little nervous, though...
Don't tell me it's because you're alone with Rinko... like that？
That's part of it, but... you see, it's kind of awkward being in my girlfriend's house.
Hmm, I see. That was it.
Do you want something to drink？
I recommend my little brother's favorite juice. Double Ramune flavor, extra dark melon flavor, strawberry jam flavor...
Okay, I'll go with that, ▲小早川＊▲.
Oh, right. Do you want some potato chips？
Yes. Do you always eat here ▲小早川＊▲？
Yeah, I can sit or lie down... Ah！ Sorry. I'm out of potato chips...
You may be fine, but Rinko is not. I should have gone to the convenience store... what should I do for dinner tonight？
Don't stare too much, are you searching my house？
I just thought it looked like you, ▲小早川＊▲.
I don't want you to judge me as "like" something.
Hmm, so this is the image of Rinko in your mind...
Hey, what do you think if Rinko lived alone...？
Because you can come and visit more easily.
Hmm, but there's more things to worry about. The world is a dangerous place, you know.
Why don't you just keep an eye on me 24/7？
I don't know, I just can't help but notice the smell of other people's rooms, you know？
Smell, huh... yeah, that's something you tend to do sometimes.
Lemme take on the smell of your room, ▲小早川＊▲...
Hey, don't do that. Nose breathing is prohibited.
What is the first thing you do when you get home？
What do you wear？ Are you the type to change into loungewear right away？
Well, if it was a uniform. What about you, ▲小早川＊▲は？
I think Rinko changes clothes rather quickly... When she is alone.
(I see, now you're still wearing the same clothes you went out in.)
What？ You've been staring around since a while ago.
You're about to trace it with your fingertips and say, "Rinko-san, there's so much dust".
Haha, that's not true. I was just looking at how clean it was.
Even with this, you can't see quite as much...
Hey, how does it feel to come to your girlfriend's room？
You're happy, you're embarrassed, you're all kinds of things.
Of course I'm happy. It makes me feel special.
Obviously. This kind of thing is special only for my boyfriend, of course.
Is there anything you would like to do when you come to Rinko's room？
I'm not going to do it.
Hey, isn't there something？ Other than sexual harassment.
(For now, please forget about sexual harassment...)
Oh, fashion magazines. What kind of things do you read, ▲小早川＊▲？
Wait. Don't touch those without permission.
"The fashion feature you want to show your boyfriend"... you're checking these things out seriously, aren't you？
Don't look at it. That's because I just wanted the appendix.
Say something... It's awkward when you break off a conversation.
Yeah. It's just the two of us in a room, you know？ You get nervous when it's quiet.
You don't have a large amount of CDs.
Rinko doesn't have a lot. My dad has a great deal.
Yes, he has many CDs, but it's the vinyl records he has in his collection.
Heh, I kind of admire that.
I don't mind, but... I try to do it in moderation.
Is this your entire collection of books, ▲小早川＊▲？
I have them in other rooms, but mostly. I know it's pretty small.
Well, you're a student. That's what the library is for.
That's what the Library Committee is for, isn't it？
It's like all the books in the library are from your collection, ▲小早川＊▲.
I wonder if we can make this room a little more mature.
Because I haven't made any major changes in the last few years. Like a change of scenery as we grow.
Come to think of it, there aren't many cat goods or anything like that.
It's not my hobby to put a lot of stuffed animals in a row.
When I go back home, you take them out and play with them.
You are too delusional. Hah, I'm worried about you.
I'm still a little uncomfortable with you being in this room.
I'm feeling a bit queasy about it, too.
And yet, when you leave, it all goes back to Rinko's room as usual.
Does your little brother come into your room ▲小早川＊▲？
He does. When Rinko is relaxed, he often attacks.
Attacks, huh... you must not feel relaxed.
I told them not to enter without permission, but there were signs that someone had broken in. Well, it can't be helped.
That place... where you're sitting. That's Rinko's spot.
Okay, I'll put you in your place.
Yeah. That kind of thing is not good.
(I have a fixed position in your room, ▲小早川＊▲...)
Hey, I'd like to see your photo album ▲小早川＊▲.
I don't mind... if it's just the album.
Ah, there was one like this.
It's kind of nostalgic. It's mysterious.
I don't remember that... Rinko's life has been through a lot.
This is the one you took the other day.
Oh, this is the one I took before.
At this time, you were making a funny face.
Huh？ I think this was recent.
I'm embarrassed by the old photos, but I'm also embarrassed by the recent ones...
I don't remember seeing anything like this... voyeur？
Hey, isn't there something weird about this picture？
Look at this place... faces！ Kidding, did I surprise you？
Hmm, I need to sort out my photos a bit.
This photo... must be my imagination.
Hehe... sorry, I'm laughing as I recall.
Wait, you don't have to take it so seriously.
Our first visit to a Shrine. I remember how many people were there.
Oh... Valentine's Day. You shouldn't take pictures of these things.
White Day pictures, huh. At this time... hehe, it's okay.
Christmas, huh... Take another photo next time.
That's my birthday photo. Hehe, it was the best day of my life since you celebrated my birthday.
This is from... your birthday. What do you want next？
It's nice to have pictures left over from special occasions.
Rinko, you know... she doesn't think she'll ever forget this moment.
Hey, you remember this day, don't you？
This picture reminds me of... various things.
I hope there will be more photos.
I think it's good to do something like this once in a while. Like a memory appreciation party？
It was interesting. Will watch again.
That's a pretty good shot. You mean the subject was good？
The album appreciation party was nice. Let's do it again.
Okay, that's it. Let me know if you want to see it again.
Geez... how long are you going to watch it？ You like it too much...
All I have are happy memories, yes.
I'll put it away now. If you want to see it again, you can come again.
Photos are nice, but... see, the real thing is here.
Hey... how about studying together sometime？
Study, huh... I see. If you want to, fine.
Why？ This is not the library.
Hey, can I take a picture？
Now？ You really like that. Okay.
Hey, don't you want to see the album？
Yeah, I want to see it
Ah, I see. I won't show it to you anymore even if you ask me to...
Hey, why don't we study once in a while？ Like high school students.
Can we do it another time？
Hah... that way, you'll cry on the tests, you know？
Hey, do you still have a camera？
Sure. Let me take some pictures
Wait a minute. I'll go get some potato chips.
Oh... I'll be waiting for you then.
(...it's oddly nerve wracking to be alone.)
Hey, Rinko-chan. Can I say hi to your friend？
Hey mom, what are you doing？
That's okay, Rinko will take care of that.
(I guess she's wondering what's going on in the room.)
Kai, I have a visitor now, so maybe later.
Hey, just go back to your room.
(Looks you can't hold a candle to your brother, ▲小早川＊▲.)
Onee-chan, let's play a game, shall we？
Hey, onee-chan, look, look. A new robot！
Kai, your sister is busy right now because her boyfriend is here. Don't interrupt her, okay？
(It's uncomfortable to hear the whole story...)
Ah, Kai！ Those are onee- chan's potato chips
Hey, it says "Ri" here. This one is onee-chan's snack.
Okay, you can eat those. But don't do it next time.
(You're so sweet... you even write your name on the potato chips.)
It's not that... um, how long are you going to stay inside？
Oh, my bad... Well, I knew that.
Haha, it's nothing. Sorry to interrupt.
Kai, what's wrong. What are you doing there？
Well... dad told me to go ask onee-chan what they are doing.
It's okay, you didn't do anything wrong, Kai.
This guy doesn't do anything while Rinko is gone.
Sorry to keep you waiting. What were you doing？
Hey, I was wondering what I should wear on our next date. Can I ask my boyfriend's opinion？
Ah, I see... then don't complain about how I dress.
(Well, you don't have to say that...)
Hehe. Well, then, wait a minute.
I'd like to see something else
Really？ But, while you're at it, take a look at the other ones.
How about this one？ I hope it suits me.
Oh, it looks great on you！
I'd like to see neat and clean clothes
Yay. Hehe... I'm kind of embarrassed.
Ah, I see... So what do you like？
A one piece might be good
Hmm... I see. I get it.
I see... Well, don't get your hopes up and wait.
What's that... seriously？ ...I don't know if I have something like that.
Here you go... How about this one？
This is what it looks like...
It's like this, so what do you think？
The first one is the best
So you like this kind of thing, huh？ Well, I guess it's settled then.
Mmm-hmm. So this is the kind of thing you like... I'll think about it.
That's what bothers me the most... No complaints allowed then.
Oh, that was fun. How about you？
Of course, I had fun too. But I'd better go home soon.
Oh no, it's that time of the day...
It's true. I should go home, indeed.
Yes. Okay, I'll see you out.
Hmm... You know what, maybe I'd like you to stay a little longer.
Yay. I knew you would say that.
I see... Well, it can't be helped. Come again.
Isn't this the first time you've come to play like this？
There's nothing to see here, but make yourself at home.
Yes, I will. I'll do so even if you don't tell me.
Ah, I feel like I'm home.
Haha, I guess you're all used to it by now.
Well... that's because it's my room.
Oh, I get it. Because it's not very pretty！
Hey, what's so special about this room？
Special？ You mean like interior design？
Yes. I was wondering what the concept was.
I haven't thought about the concept or anything...
So, are you ready to let Rinko take care of it？ I'll make it a rockin' room.
What if Rinko says she doesn't want to go home？
Haha, you're not going to make me answer from the beginning.
Hey, is this what a man's room looks like？
Maybe？ I don't think it's such a special room.
Dad's room isn't even as refreshing as this one.
Well, it's okay, my dad's room and your room, that's all I know.
Did you clean up the place, by any chance？
It's not really a big cleanup.
Hmm, I guess it's okay for people to have a secret thing or two.
Oh, by the way, today is...
They're doing a special on animal shows, a cat special.
You want to turn on the TV？
Not now, because it should have been recorded properly unless my little brother is playing a prank on me.
Sure, but what are using it for？
The contents of a computer are a person's hobbies, tastes, and personality.
Nothing... but let's do something else instead.
Heh, I hear you research dates by looking at that kind of thing.
Well, yeah. This is a ramen special, though.
There it is, why do boys like ramen so much？
How many girls have entered this room, besides Rinko？
Yeah. I'm not going to lie to you.
Hey, can Rinko put her stuff down here？
Various... books I've finished reading, teaching materials I don't use, etc...
Hehe. But you know, they say it's nice to have more of your girlfriend's things in your room.
I was kind of amused when I imagined it.
Why do you do it, ▲小早川＊▲？
I'm keeping quiet because you're keeping quiet. What about you？
Does this mean we're on the same page too？
I have a feeling it's not the same, but it's nice to know that... I can keep my mouth shut and still feel safe.
Hey, which do you like better, being together like this or being alone in a room？
Well, it's more fun being together.
Do you ever feel like you're in the way？ Like, you want some alone time.
It's not that I don't have time alone, it's just that I prefer to be with you.
Hmm... well, I won't hold back.
A girl in my class, you know, she went to visit her boyfriend.
When she went there, she said she was a little taken back by the many pictures of himself on the wall.
A picture of himself, or a picture of his girlfriend？
It makes me want to dye this room in Rinko's color.
(Ah, you mean dyeing it to your taste, ▲小早川＊▲...)
Is there anything you would like your girlfriend to do when she comes to your house？
I'm not good at cleaning, laundry, and many other things, though.
Haha, thank you. I'm glad you said that.
You're only as good as you are... hehe.
It feels good to have big windows, doesn't it？
Yes. It will get more sun, and the wind will be able to pass through.
I like it. Rinko's room doesn't have a big window.
And if you had one, you'd be lazing under the sunset.
That's what you think. I'm not stepping out of my room.
Not as much as I could...
You shouldn't do that... I'm pretty proud of the fact that I ate my boyfriend's home-cooked food, that's a pretty good story.
Okay, you don't have to brag about it.
When you are at home, are you a music listener？
Rinko keeps it on when she is in her room. It's headphones, though.
I know, I have neighbors, and it's hard to turn up the volume.
Yes, I'd love to live in a house where I could listen to punk until I feel like blowing up, wouldn't you？
Your room doesn't have much stuff, does it？
I think it could use a little more life.
(Is that good？ or, is it bad？)
Do you want to play my newly acquired game？
Okay. I'll get to it right away.
Are you going to challenge Rinko to another game？ You have guts.
I bought a DVD of the new movie. Do you want to watch it？
Okay. So, what do you want to watch？
...I don't really want to watch one.
It was more than I could have imagined. I can't wait to see it again.
Well, this is the kind of thing I like once in a while.
Hah... isn't it like giving back time？
Ah, I have a new CD. Do you want to listen to it？
Do you want to listen to some music？
Yeah, that's nice. What do you have？
Wow, this is a nice style！ You have good taste.
Hey, do you want to play some games？
Hey, can we watch some DVDs？
I don't know if I want to watch one
Hah, I can't believe it's that time already... I'm having so much fun I'm losing track of time.
It's true... Wanna go home now？
I think I'll go home now...
If you're late, they'll worry about you
Yes. I think I'll be okay for a little while longer.
I knew it... better stop for today.
You're right. It's a little sad, though.
Rinko would like to stay with you a little longer, though.
I see, then of course it's fine.
Well then, I'll take you home.
Hey... aren't you a bit hungry？
Yes, come to think of it.
Hmm... I learned a new dish. Want to try it？
Let's go out to eat today
Rinko can make some food for you... if you don't mind.
Do you want to go out for something to eat？
Alright. I'll give it a shot.
I'm rooting for you in the challenge...
If I don't have enough material, I'll run out and buy some.
...I can't help it. You really are a caring boyfriend.
I don't want to. I'm not in the mood to cook.
...I see. Too bad, but lets go eat out.
I went to the trouble of learning it... idiot.
So where do you want to go？
Yeah, that's good. Let's go with that.
Now that I'm fired up, I'm ready to get started.
I just thought it would be nice to do something like this once in a while...
Do you want to make any request？
I'm in the mood for Japanese food
I'm not sure of the genre...
I'd like to eat some ▲料理ジャンル▲.
I knew you'd say that. That's Rinko's specialty.
That's fine. I can do that.
Well, I can do it from memory... Don't get your hopes up, just wait and see.
I've never made anything like that before... Don't laugh if I make something weird.
Hmm？ ...I really think I'm missing something.
With this, all right... it's finished.
Here you go. There's power in it.
Hmm, maybe I should sweeten it up.
Yeah, smells good. Sorry to keep you waiting.
Hehe. This tableware is the same as Rinko's. Aren't you happy？
What do you want me to make next？ I'll think of something for you.
I'm in the mood for Japanese food.
I'm not sure of the genre...
I'd like to eat some ▲料理ジャンル▲.
It's the worst... the faucet is broken.
Uh, sorry. Are your clothes okay？
My bad. Then use the shower.
I don't know... I'm feeling a bit cold.
Are you okay？ You can use the bathroom if you want to get warmed up.
It's raining terribly, I'm soaking wet...
You look like you're going to catch a cold. Go take a shower.
Maybe I should. Then I'll borrow it.
(I'll try to be as unaware of it as possible...)
What should I do about my clothes？
In the meantime, you'll just have to bear with that.
This？ I'm a little, you know, embarrassed...
I see... I'll try to find something better.
Phew... that's refreshing. Did you wait properly and maturely？
Haha, yeah. I was also restless.
Thanks. It looks like I'm going to stay the night.
I knew it was only my imagination. Forget it.
I'm back to life. Hey... go inside too. You'll catch a cold, you know？
